evince (0.4.0-4) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Loic Minier ]
  * Add a get-orig-source target to retrieve the upstream tarball.

  [ Marc 'HE' Brockschmidt ]
  * debian/patches/20_fix_multiple_copies.patch:
     Backported from upstream, allowing people to print more than one copy of
     one document in one go. (Closes: #401172)
  * debian/patches/21_fix_doc_typo.patch:
     Fix typo in documentation. (Closes: #320266)
  * debian/evince.mime:
     Add entries for DVI and DjVu documents. (Closes: 337784)
  * debian/control: 
    - Note that evince's PDF rendering is done by poppler, not
      by XPdf (Closes: #332197)
    - Add dependency on gs-esp | gs, as we need it for postscript
      rendering. (Closes: 335108)
    - Version build-dependencies on gnome-doc-utils and libdjvulibre-dev
      (Closes: #332633)
  * debian/copyright: Update FSF address

 -- Marc 'HE' Brockschmidt <he@debian.org>  Fri, 12 Jan 2007 13:56:37 +0100

